import React from 'react' import './header.css' import {useEffect, useState} from 'react'; function header() { useEffect(() => { const tab = document.querySelector(".move"), topbar = tab.querySelector(".moving_header"); function onDrag({movementX, movementY}){ let getStyle = window.getComputedStyle(tab); let leftVal = parseInt(getStyle.left); let topVal = parseInt(getStyle.top); tab.style.left = `${leftVal + movementX}px`; tab.style.top = `${topVal + movementY}px`; } topbar.addEventListener("mousedown", ()=>{ topbar.classList.add("active"); topbar.addEventListener("mousemove", onDrag); }); document.addEventListener("mouseup", ()=>{ topbar.classList.remove("active"); topbar.removeEventListener("mousemove", onDrag); }); }, []); return (
